        "example": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Consider the sentence: ",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "preformatted",
            "text": "I resent that letter.",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "This could mean either that one sent the letter again, or that one has a feeling of resentment towards it. So, the sentence could be a boobytrap. If you concluded, falsely, on the basis of the sentence, that the speaker sent the letter again, then you would have committed a fallacy of Accent.",
